graph TB
    subgraph "Notebook Controller (Kubeflow)"
        NotebookReconciler[Notebook Reconciler<br/>Controller]
        CullingReconciler[Culling Reconciler<br/>Controller]
        MetricsServer[Metrics Server<br/>:8080/TCP HTTP]
        HealthProbe[Health Probe<br/>:8081/TCP HTTP]

        NotebookReconciler -->|monitors idle time| CullingReconciler
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        NotebookBeta[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1beta1]
        NotebookAlpha[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "Managed Resources"
        StatefulSet[StatefulSet<br/>apps/v1]
        Service[Service<br/>ClusterIP]
        VirtualService[VirtualService<br/>networking.istio.io]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>Optional]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Optional]
    end

    subgraph "Managed Workloads"
        NotebookPod[Jupyter Notebook Pod<br/>:8888/TCP HTTP]
    end

    %% User interaction
    User[User/Dashboard] -->|creates| NotebookCR
    NotebookCR -->|watched by| NotebookReconciler
    NotebookBeta -.->|conversion webhook| NotebookCR
    NotebookAlpha -.->|conversion webhook| NotebookCR

    %% Reconciler creates resources
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates/updates| StatefulSet
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates/updates| Service
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates when USE_ISTIO=true| VirtualService

    %% StatefulSet creates pods
    StatefulSet -->|manages| NotebookPod

    %% Service routes to pods
    Service -->|routes to| NotebookPod

    %% Culling checks pods
    CullingReconciler -->|queries /api/kernels| NotebookPod
    CullingReconciler -->|adds stopped annotation| NotebookCR

    %% External dependencies
    NotebookReconciler -->|RBAC operations| K8sAPI
    VirtualService -->|configured via| Istio
    Prometheus -->|scrapes /metrics| MetricsServer

    %% Styling
    style NotebookReconciler fill:#4a90e2
    style CullingReconciler fill:#4a90e2
    style MetricsServer fill:#4a90e2
    style HealthProbe fill:#4a90e2
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623
    style NotebookBeta fill:#f5a623
    style NotebookAlpha fill:#f5a623
    style StatefulSet fill:#7ed321
    style Service fill:#7ed321
    style VirtualService fill:#7ed321
    style K8sAPI fill:#999
    style Istio fill:#999
    style Prometheus fill:#999
    style NotebookPod fill:#d4af37
